      "side": 1,
      "message": "AFAICT, you need to insert AliasingBarriers to make sure everything is synchronized properly, which I didn\u0027t include in this CL. Other than that I haven\u0027t seen any restrictions.\n\nAnd I\u0027m not sure there\u0027s an equivalent to the mutable format but I can check.",
