      "message": "So looks like for SRVs you can set a compatible format on the D3D12_SHADER_RESOURCE_VIEW_DESC. And for UAV there is a format on the D3D12_UNORDERED_ACCESS_VIEW_DESC. I feel like you can just use those to create different views instead of dealing with aliased resources. But I may be missing something in my quick search",
